s. Identifiers can help other people understand exactly what you mean, and they allow computers to interpret your data in a meaningful way (i.e., computers that are searching for your data or trying to automatically integrate them).","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"UjnbfnTzVf"}],"key":"yKPUF0THlT"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Identifiers are essential to the human-machine interoperation that is key to the vision of ","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"QcwZdHjigc"},{"type":"link","url":"https://www.dtls.nl/5825-2/","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Open Science","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"lKPxfyKVnj"}],"urlSource":"https://www.dtls.nl/5825-2/","key":"xtQ5BlZsIZ"},{"type":"text","value":". In addition, identifiers will help others to properly cite your work when reusing your data.","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"Du1FWuWMhO"}],"key":"hL1sV5Ow9H"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"link","url":"https://www.go-fair.org/fair-principles/f1-meta-data-assigned-globally-unique-persistent-identifiers/","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"inlineCode","value":"F1: (Meta) data are assigned globally unique and persistent identifiers","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"SeeW2L9Ifp"}],"urlSource":"https://www.go-fair.org/fair-principles/f1-meta-data-assigned-globally-unique-persistent-identifiers/","key":"XscRs4anVQ"}],"key":"F33gnpZ6zE"}],"key":"b41gp230wf"}],"key":"AyppLZZHk0"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}},"footer":{"navigation":{"prev